Finance firms provide QR codes for immediate internship applications, and consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables. Career counselors assist by redirecting unsure students toward applicable industries. Event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards at the entrance. Meanwhile, a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, and friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. Students exit with tote bags and a stack of business cards, while the dean stops by to thank recruiters for supporting the university.
